<list id="fs-id1830388" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic"><item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>Evaluate</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mtext>when</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.2em"/><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>−4</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/>
If you missed this problem, review <link target-id="fs-id1166761429575" document="m53013"/>.</item>
