   <entry><span class="token">ⓑ</span> Substitute −4 for x in the equation to determine if it is true.</entry>
<entry><media id="eip-id1168469681480" alt="."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_03_05_009_img-02.png"/></media></entry>
