<para id="fs-id1586493"><emphasis effect="bold">Cookie packaging</emphasis> A package of <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>51 cookies</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> has <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> equal rows of cookies. Find the number of cookies in each row, <m:math><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:math> by solving the equation <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>c</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>51</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id2708025">
